+
+- Final release of the 0-5-* versions. Next will be a complete rewrite
+  of many features. This release contains several bugfixes related to
+  directory renaming.
+
+
+v0-5-10-pre6:
+
+- Lots of cleanup and several bugfixes related to directory deleting
+
